  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3105620/extras/28f1e0b117c6b8d26bba7c791df9f34a.avif?t=1758838289\" width=616 height=144 /></span>Everseeker is a Hidden Object game and a charming experience of exploration and discovery, where your goal is to find 100 small insects hidden in a picturesque village of adorable bunnies. All the art is carefully hand-drawn, providing a relaxing and immersive atmosphere. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take some time for yourself and dive into this wonderful world. We all need a break from time to time, and there's nothing better than a calm and charming game to help us unwind. We hope to see you soon <3 <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3105620/extras/32df70dcb88ecc967c7ac748fbc385f0.poster.avif?t=1758838289\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3105620/extras/32df70dcb88ecc967c7ac748fbc385f0.webm?t=1758838289\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3105620/extras/32df70dcb88ecc967c7ac748fbc385f0.mp4?t=1758838289\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3105620/extras/e8e04770cffd521f6fd6494773d25cfe.webp?t=1758838289\" width=618 height=22 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FEATURES</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >100 creatures to find</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hidden secrets</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Beautifully hand-drawn scenery</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Achievements</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Speedrun game mode</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Controller support</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gamedev comments</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >CUSTOMIZATION</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3105620/extras/13b58b4c1bf349dd2c8e7ead35015d33.poster.avif?t=1758838289\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3105620/extras/13b58b4c1bf349dd2c8e7ead35015d33.webm?t=1758838289\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3105620/extras/13b58b4c1bf349dd2c8e7ead35015d33.mp4?t=1758838289\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3105620/extras/f496fd1b3e4994c9e0d2373c64f11e9a.poster.avif?t=1758838289\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3105620/extras/f496fd1b3e4994c9e0d2373c64f11e9a.webm?t=1758838289\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3105620/extras/f496fd1b3e4994c9e0d2373c64f11e9a.mp4?t=1758838289\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
